Definition eq (x y: t) := NE.eq (fst x) (fst y) /\ (forall ge sp b ofs, nlive ge sp (snd x) b ofs <-> nlive ge sp (snd y) b ofs).

Lemma eq_sym: forall x y, eq x y -> eq y x.
unfold eq; destruct x, y; simpl.

unfold eq; destruct x, y, z; simpl.
Definition beq (x y: t) : bool := NE.beq (fst x) (fst y) && nmem_beq (snd x) (snd y).

Definition ge (x y: t) : Prop := NE.ge (fst x) (fst y) /\ (forall ge sp b ofs, nlive ge sp (snd y) b ofs -> nlive ge sp (snd x) b ofs).
Lemma ge_refl: forall x y, eq x y -> ge x y.
unfold eq, ge; destruct x, y; simpl.
Lemma ge_trans: forall x y z, ge x y -> ge y z -> ge x z.
unfold ge; destruct x, y, z; simpl.
Lemma ge_bot: forall x, ge x bot.
unfold ge, bot; destruct x; simpl.
Definition lub (x y: t) : t := (NE.lub (fst x) (fst y), nmem_lub (snd x) (snd y)).

unfold ge; destruct x, y; simpl; split.
Lemma ge_lub_right: forall x y, ge (lub x y) y.
unfold ge; destruct x, y; simpl; split.
